                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8075" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0242</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2886 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">代际传承何以顺利？梅花生物高管激励机制的优化之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> How can intergenerational inheritance go smoothly? The way to optimize the incentive mechanism of senior executives of Meifa</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨海燕，刘哲灵</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广西大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">梅花生物科技集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家族企业；代际传承；高管激励；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Family business, intergenerational inheritance, executive motivation, corporate governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">我国家族企业已进入代际传承高峰期，高管激励是家族治理的重要手段，在家族企业代际传承中发挥着重要作用，是财务管理、公司治理教学的重要内容之一。本案例从2011年梅花生物代际传承开始入手，叙述了梅花生物代际传承过程及其高管激励现状、代际传承后高管激励的优化措施，并从二代继承人权威构建、高管团队勤勉义务履行、公司绩效表现三个方面阐述了高管激励机制的优化效果。让学生系统的了解家族环境的变化如何影响代际传承模式的选择，代际传承模式又如何影响高管激励机制的设计；全面掌握激励对象、激励方式、激励强度等高管激励机制的设计与应用；深入理解家族企业代际传承后高管激励机制的优化之道及对二代继承人权威构建、增强高管团队勤勉义务和提升公司绩效的影响。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">China&#39;s family enterprises have entered the peak period of intergenerational inheritance, and executive incentive is an important tool of family governance, which plays an important role in the intergenerational inheritance of family enterprises and is one of the important contents of teaching financial management and corporate governance. This case starts from the intergenerational inheritance of Meifa in 2011, describes the process of intergenerational inheritance of Meifa and its current situation of executive incentive, the optimization measures of executive incentive after intergenerational inheritance, and elaborates the optimization effect of executive incentive mechanism from three aspects: the construction of authority of second generation successors, the fulfillment of diligence obligation of executive team, and the performance of company performance. Students will understand systematically how the change of family environment affects the choice of intergenerational inheritance mode and how the intergenerational inheritance mode affects the design of executive incentive mechanism; comprehensively grasp the design and application of executive incentive mechanism such as incentive object, incentive mode and incentive intensity; deeply understand the way of optimizing executive incentive mechanism after intergenerational inheritance of family enterprises and the influence on the construction of authority of second generation heirs, enhancing the diligence obligation of executive team and The impact on the authority building of the second generation successors, enhancing the diligence of the executive team and improving the performance of the company.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《公司理财》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">代际传承模式；委托代理理论；利益相关者理论；高管激励机制；社会情感财富理论；权威认同构建；需求层次理论；激励理论；家族治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
